IMDBQuery
=========

The point of this tool is query IMDB to gather some fun facts
like "what's the average rating of movies that Pierce
Brosnan appeared in?" and "which Stallone movie scored best
and which one worst?"

Requirements
============
A normal PHP 5+ install with curl, DOM* and tidy modules
installed should do the trick.

Running
=======
Check the check.php script - it shows how to run the scripts

Testing
=======
There are unit tests supplied for most of the classes - check
the /tests/ folder. You'll need PHPUnit to run them.

Contact
=======
If you want to get in contact with the author, write to:
peter@plphp.dk
